{"tha-ap270:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap270:0.2":"Padumukkhipavagga ","tha-ap270:0.3":"8 Salalapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap270:1.1":"“Candabhaganaditire, ","tha-ap270:1.2":"ahosim kinnaro tada; ","tha-ap270:1.3":"Vipassim addasam buddham, ","tha-ap270:1.4":"ramsijalasamakulam. ","tha-ap270:2.1":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap270:2.2":"paramaya ca pitiya; ","tha-ap270:2.3":"Paggayha salalam puppham, ","tha-ap270:2.4":"vipassim okirim aham. ","tha-ap270:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap270:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap270:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap270:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap270:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap270:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap270:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap270:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma salalapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap270:6.1":"Salalapupphiyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}